div.div:
1. RMM service scans the RMM table nightly for records that are
eligible for disposition within xx days, generating a “Disposition
Eligible” report.
2. Eva dashboard presents this data to the users each morning.
Data is broken down by Dataset.
3. IMOs drill into the report and review the nature of the dataset and
a sampling of objects to validate they were correctly tagged.
a. If the items are correctly tagged, the IMO moves
forward.
b. If the items are not correctly tagged, the IMO reviews
the data, and reviews the rules used to apply the RCS
value to determine where the issue stems from.i. The IMO applies the correct RCS value tothose updates which updates the dispositionelable date.ii. The IMO updates the rule to correct for anyissues. This updates “date forward” records.iii. The IMO with input from leadership, runs the4. IMO notifies the data owner that there are xxxx files eligable for
dispostion and provides the owner with a link to the dataset and
the eligible items. The owner has xx days to review the objects.
a. If the owner concurs, the DMO notes the concurrence
and performs a bulk update to the RMM data.i. RMM posts a message to one or morequeues.ii. The hosting system acknowledges themessage.iii. The acknowledgement is stored in the in theRMM Tableiv. The host system then takes action.1. Delete2. Transferv. The host system publishes the action back onthe queue and updates RMMb. If the owner does not concuri. The IMO would work with leadership to acceptthe non-concurrence and update thedisposition eligible dateii. The IMO and leadership would notify theowner that the data in fact must be deletedand would override the Owners position. TheDMO notes the non-concurrence, adds theoverriding leadership decision, and performs abulk update to the RMM data.1. RMM posts a message to one ormore queues.2. The hosting system acknowledgesthe message.3. The acknowledgement is stored inthe in the RMM Table4. The host system then takes action.a. Deleteb. Transfer5. The host system publishes theaction back on the queue andupdates RMM
